<br />
<br />I'm not trying to rain on anybody's parade, but this sort of topic pops up from time to time (maybe more commonly on other forums), and nothing ever comes of it. Most people who can do something productive shy away from working on ambitious projects started by strangers when nothing is shown up front. If you want people to even so much as respond, post links to past projects, a detailed outline or plan for your project, or at the very least some proposals.

		

		</td>
